# CHANGELOG - APPEND ONLY
# Object: append-only-registry-rule

## v1.0 (2025-02-23)
### Initial Release

#### Added
- Append-only principle cho toàn bộ .olym registry
- Immutable spine cho 7 domain folders
- Version discipline (major/minor bump rules)
- Seal.log append-only format
- Changelog.ail append-only format
- Links.ail cross-reference model
- Master/index.clo authority pointer
- Forbidden operations list
- Pre-commit compliance check
- 10-year stability goal

#### Why
- Đảm bảo deterministic loading
- Tránh overwrite gây mất seal integrity
- Hỗ trợ poly-ledger anchoring
- Chuẩn bị cho T3C/Hace enable
- Audit trail hoàn chỉnh

#### Dependencies
- constitution/poly-ledger-anchor-law.clo
- constitution/seal-integrity-law.clo (pending)
- protocol/registry-freeze-protocol.clo (pending)

#### Compliance
- Follows AIL v3.1.8 (85% VI + 15% EN)
- Fractal naming: ros.rule.registry.append-only
- Lazy type: immutability_rule
